author: Joe Klarer
title: Valley Springs arm wrestler training to be world champion
text:
1 of 3 Courtesy photo 
With his prolific arm wrestling, Robbie Topie has been able to travel all over the world and gain sponsorships, like his most recent, 51 Fifty Energy Drink. Mixed martial arts fighter Nick Kohring, a Valley Springs native, is also sponsored by 51 Fifty Energy Drink. Courtesy photo 
Professional arm wrestler Robbie Topie of Valley Springs is well on his way to becoming a world champion. Courtesy photo 
Topie in action at the 9/11 Memorial Armwrestling Tournament in Bakersfield Sept. 11. featured
